column5: Got out for a beauty day to try and prepare for the salmon derby fish-off on saturday. Did well going for 9 for 10. Hope there a few more days left like this.
nice fish,sounds like you had a productive day,congrats
Nice catch---like the looks of that "chrome"
Nice catch !!!!!   good-luck in the salmon derby,let us know how you do...hope the weatherman is on your side as well...cheers
nice fish and some nice bows in there as well. Hope the trout stay off you line for the fishoff.  Bowen
AHHH LOVELY TO SEE MY BLESSED CHROME ONCE AGAIN!! NICE JOB GUYS
blinded by the chrome!!!! awesome job guys!
